Mzee Kalua's first born son, renowned environmentalist Dr Isaac Kalua, says their father suffered a heart attack.Mzee Kalua was the founding Bishop of St Stephen’s Ministry in Kitui County and also served as a lay leader and reverend of the ACK Church. Bishop David Kalua, a former State House chief gardener, who served under the late former President Daniel arap Moi, is dead.
The former prison warden was President Moi’s aide for more than 10 years.
During that period, his main responsibility was to ensure the lapel of Head of State suits were adorned with a fresh rose every day.



